From c6b52b9f8dfd0e43b54d5be55244bfc6114cf74a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Karthikeya <karthi@jovio.in>
Date: Mon, 29 Jun 2026 08:18:42 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/4] feat(api): public REST API + tenant API keys (Scale plan)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Scale plan promises 'API access for integrations' — this delivers it.

NEW: supabase/004_api_keys.sql
  api_keys table with bcrypt-hashed key storage (plaintext never
  persisted). prefix column for dashboard display (first 12 chars).
  scopes jsonb for permission granularity. mode field for live/test.
  Usage tracking (last_used_at, last_used_ip, request_count).
  Soft delete via revoked_at to preserve audit trail.
  RLS: tenant members can list (without seeing key_hash); only
  service-role can write.

NEW: api-server/src/index.ts additions
  - generateApiKey(): jvk_live_<24 random bytes base64url>
  - verifyApiKey middleware: parses Bearer, looks up by prefix (cheap
    indexed query), bcrypt.compare against candidates' hashes, checks
    expiry + revocation. Updates usage stats async (fire-and-forget).
  - requireScope(...scopes): per-route permission gate
  - publicApiLimiter: 100 req/min per apiKeyId (separate from generic
    /api limiter so a dashboard user can't burn through a customer's
    API quota)

NEW: /api/v1/* endpoints (API-key authenticated)
  GET /api/v1/calls           — paginated, cursor-based, scope: calls.read
  GET /api/v1/calls/:id       — single call detail with transcript
  GET /api/v1/appointments    — scope: appointments.read
  GET /api/v1/usage           — current month minutes used

NEW: /api/keys management (dashboard-authenticated via verifyInternal)
  POST /api/keys              — issue. Returns plaintext key ONCE.
  POST /api/keys/:id/revoke   — soft delete

Both write to audit_log (api_key.issued / api_key.revoked) for DPDP
compliance.

NEW: dashboard/app/api-keys/page.tsx
  Full UI for issuing + listing + revoking keys. One-time plaintext
  reveal modal (with clipboard copy). Scope picker (4 options with
  recommended defaults). Expiry selector (never / 30d / 90d / 1yr).
  Empty state. Stats per key (request count, last used).

Deps: bcryptjs@^2.4.3 + @types/bcryptjs@^2.4.6
